cast.overview: Follow Robbie Williams' journey from childhood, to being the youngest member of chart-topping boyband Take That, through to his unparalleled achievements as a record-breaking solo artist – all the while confronting the challenges that stratospheric fame and success can bring.
cast.title: Better Man

details.biography: Brett Sewell is a London based Dancer/Performer. He began his professional training at the Brit School of Performing Arts and Technology, he then advanced to The Urdang Academy where he studied a level 6 Diploma in Dance, continuing his training for a further three years. Throughout his training Brett has immersed himself into the Industry, giving him the opportunities to be a part of various jobs and opportunities. Brett is a hard working artist who is excited for what the future holds.
details.name: Brett Sewell
